data.description: This up/down duplex, currently owner-occupied, is a promising investment in a quiet neighborhood with convenient access to public transportation. It features two units, each with two bedrooms and one full bathroom. The main floor unit has a sunroom, and the upper-level unit comes with a patio, adding value and appeal. Each unit has a dedicated basement section for laundry and storage plus access to the detached two car garage. Separately metered and easy to rent for a great income producing property, call today!
